title: Running Australia’s premier events precinct & majors venues
itunes:title: Running Australia’s premier events precinct & majors venues
description:
Go behind-the-scenes of Australia’s premier events destination as Mark Beretta speaks to Event and Operation Managers from Sydney Olympic Park Authority, ANZ Stadium, Sydney Showground and Qudos Bank Arena.

Hear from the people who make sure the show goes on for the biggest names in entertainment and sport, ensuring people can safely access and enjoy the magic of events!

Their passion for the events industry will move you as they manage venues once used for the Games and today supporting over 5,000 events held at the Park each year.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
